{"type": "article", "id": 55422, "title": "这款一体式萃取杯，泡茶做咖啡都方便｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-19T23:14:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 51979, "name": "Kekkilä"}, {"id": 51980, "name": "Pentagon Design"}, {"id": 51981, "name": "Hannabi"}, {"id": 8469, "name": "Soma"}, {"id": 43654, "name": "LEGO"}, {"id": 51982, "name": "Kalyani Tupkary"}, {"id": 51983, "name": "Jakob Lukosch"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 203, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180719231637EeaYvs8HA0XIxFBi.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #7498a2; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #7498a2} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Brew Bottle by Soma</h3><p>专做滤水器的品牌 Soma 最近推出了一款专为咖啡和茶设计的一体式萃取杯，针对那些每天离不开咖啡和茶饮的用户，可以在家中或者办公室自己制作，且能随身携带。</p><p>这款一体式萃取杯由不含 BPA 的双层硼硅酸盐玻璃制成，有助于保持冷热饮品的温度。可重复使用的瓶子，配有不锈钢过滤器，一种用于冲泡，另一种用于冷泡萃取。网状过滤器可防止咖啡和茶的沉淀物进入萃取过程。</p><p>最重要的，不管是热水冲泡，还是冷水萃取，直至最终饮用的过程，都发生在这一个杯子里。售价 40 美元，<a href=\"https://www.drinksoma.com/cart\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231715YJvmnVNjft7u0EOM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231715c8SdBDwn9GAZPjfO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.517969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231715Ix1qDuMR2EKnBC9L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231715C0MwqxkyR1ls3mOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231715K6rH1NVIjPSvoJYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231715Hr3gNZYJCqORk2VA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.drinksoma.com/cart\" rel=\"nofollow\">Soma</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>UO_TUNE_IN by Jakob Lukosch</h3><p>德国工业设计师 Jakob Lukosch 最近为美国集合式品牌 Urban Outfitters 设计了一套音频、科技类产品 UO_TUNE_IN。</p><p>UO_TUNE_IN 是一个四件套产品，包括便携式移动电源、电源板、具有蓝牙功能的磁带式音箱以及一个便于收纳的充电电源。其特征是造型复古，虽然只是简单的几何形状，却能将人拉回一个久远的年代，又不失时尚感。售价 14.99 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.urbanoutfitters.com/search?q=UO_TUNE_IN\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231807e5Sqy0o69EGuXJ7O.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231807f8hgUoRVnDy4SGxl.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231807mGs9wQZNt6dUrha3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231807be0xThEtRaZm2S9N.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231807h5Knb8pzeJR9NSwj.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807192318085YUlFJA4wjBo9h8p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666786\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/65168445/UO_TUNE_IN-Collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Box Hyperactive collection by Hannabi</h3><p>你还记得小时候用七巧板制作的色彩缤纷的作品吗？位于布达佩斯的设计公司 Hannabi ，最近推出了一个模块化家具系列 Box Hyperactive，允许用户自定义沙发的每个元素，包括高度、靠背、扶手、配件，结构方式、沙发饰面、靠垫和金属配件等等。</p><p>如果你不知道如何开始构思一款沙发的话，Hannabi 还提供了各种模型来拓展你的设计思维。售价1726 欧元起，<a href=\"https://shop.hannabisofa.com/hannabi-kanapek-fotelek-80/box-hyperactivity-83\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231900Pq3KMm4YkjS8Dtvl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018071923190091rcHxZAPFLqyS6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807192319003DtM25WLHxInguQX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231900UMKAbEmy4SiHsWDR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018071923190064VEx1cDsGnWvPJk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231900JCQdG91I4Kvyxgzr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719231902niX3EdYOUwDt8QNc.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://shop.hannabisofa.com/hannabi-kanapek-fotelek-80/box-hyperactivity-83\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hannabi</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>FURNITURE FOR YOUR PLANT FRIENDS by Pentagon Design for Kekkilä</h3><p>在家里种上一两株植物，总会让空间显得格外有生气。但并不是所有人都喜欢把一个个花盆摆在地上，给生活空间添上几分杂乱。</p><p>最近，Pentagon Design 工作室为芬兰园艺公司 Kekkilä 设计的绿色系列家居用品，试图为用户喜爱的植物，提供一个充足、适合的生长空间。</p><p>这组产品包括搁架、收纳箱、梯子等等，将种植空间分散在各个产品之间。它们占用的尺寸与标准家具占据的尺寸相同，用户可以自行搭配植物适合与什么样的物品摆在一起。部分产品还包含内置照明，可帮助植物在室内生长，同时为您的房间提供照明和氛围。售价 119 欧元起，<a href=\"https://www.kekkila.fi/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719232018qg7NsdX3fcQvwuWh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807192320187zSQqWtZpc3N5HaC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719232018lE2bADioPj4JI3GU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.618095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719232018KBWzReyFjmHTwODq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719232019IPci3Os5htS0adUu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719232019RriYPqIWEwbAs68G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.kekkila.fi/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kekkilä</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Flip Scale by Kalyani Tupkary</h3><p>相信大家都有过这样的经验：想要测量一段长度时，直尺却不够长，用卷尺的话，一个人又不太好操作，而且卷尺的长度也是有限的。</p><p>设计师 Kalyani Tupkary 针对这个通病，设计了一把名为 Flip Scale 的直尺，虽然只有 15 厘米长，却可以方便地测量任何距离。这把尺子乍看起来和我们平常用的直尺没什么不同，但除了上半部分的刻度以外，下半部分却是分成两半的，在两侧以轴承的方式与上半部分相连，可以 360 度旋转。</p><p>尺子采用聚碳酸酯制作，边框和转轴使用不锈钢制作。数字条有红黄蓝三色可选。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719233241dL1a80cOfqT7kCYr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561129\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807192321186N3UB5HugKDOVX1T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.160000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719232118nEHB15WshU9S4gbt.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719232118k95FETGJN64xly20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807192321217psAoOEDMcwVfC3x.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719232122D2GFq8pQseuXYOc0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.kalyanitupkary.com/#/flip/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kalyani Tupkary</a></p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>James Bond Aston Martin DB5 Creator Expert Model Kit by LEGO</h3><p>乐高获得授权，为 007 特工詹姆斯邦德的经典座驾阿斯顿马丁 DB5 开发一款专业车模。这是一辆由 1290 块复制件组装成的 1964 年的秘密特工招牌跑车。</p><p>这款可拼装的玩具足够以假乱真，包括这款车细节之处的豪华感和多功能的配件。走近这款车模，内部装载一部可撤销记录的电脑，并在车门上装有电话。为了忠诚于 DB5，车模装载一部 6 缸直列式发动机，撞色银的前脸并拥有后尾处的缓冲管。装有模塑的银色边框轮毂，和前后的阿斯顿马丁标志。这款模型售价 150 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719233146dpRA5eiPObsG3q6E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719233146Xa847tczBQh3bdOZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666139\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719233147eglhsZ3xroKLidHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719233147EMHeKN6qV2mLs0wF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719233150EXAS79IQMvaljDJg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719233152v17tesPB8Mpi3ZyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180719233204UhufB0Iswo2cmTiN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：LEGO</figcaption></figure></div>"}